Date: Wed, 22 Mar 2023 22:45:42 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] pwm: iqs620a: Explicitly set .polarity in .get_state()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1012628
